                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130">Heinricus</persName> divina
                        favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si sanctis ac
                        venerabilibus locis eo, quae ab antecessoribus nostris collata sunt,
                        corroborare studuerimus et de his, que nostri iuris sunt, concedere
                        satagimus, aeterne vite emolumentum adipisci ac presentis status soliditatem
                        propensius augmentari non titubamus. Idcirco omnium fidelium sanctae dei
                        aecclesiae nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, Vv. <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Burgi #Houses #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Decima #Public_exactions #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/301">domini et salvatoris nostri Iesu
                            Christi</orgName> militantes in <placeName ref="#places/737">monte
                            Amate</placeName> nobis lacrimabiliter protulisse, quod famis ac
                        nuditatis indigentia ibidem deo servire non possent, eo quod <rs
                            key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> et <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">celle</rs>,
                        quae a precessoribus ad sumptum eorum conlate sunt, a pravis fuissent
                        distracte hominibus. Nos quidem pro dei amore animarumque nostrarum remedio,
                        quoniam idem coenobium in nostram devenerat potestatem ac proprietatem, res
                        et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">predia</rs>, quae a nostris precessoribus
                        collata sunt et confirmata ac corroborata, confirmare et corroborare
                        studuimus et <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">de
                            nostris iuris proprietate in monachorum sumptum</rs> cortes et cellas
                        contulimus, quatinus sedulo orationes pro nobis <rs key="#marriage"
                            >coniugeque</rs> nostra <persName key="#Queen #marriage"
                            ref="#people/131">Cunigunda</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">regina</rs> ibidem ad dominum dirigatur. Igitur cortes et
                        cellas, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massaricia</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">familiamque utriusque sexus</rs>, quae actenus
                        tenuerunt, omniaque precepta ab antecessoribus nostris conlata omniaque
                        instrumenta confirmamus pleniterque corroboramus, et quoniam prefatum
                        coenobium in nostram devenit potestatem et proprietatem, et quae a pravis
                        ablata sunt hominibus et alia, quibus indigentia explere valeant, in usum
                        fratrum per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus donamus atque largimus,
                        videlicet <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2312">Rotam cardosam, quae nunc <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1972">Burgoricho</placeName> nuncupatur</geogName>, et
                        medietatem curte <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2313"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1973">sancti Sebastiani</placeName></geogName> et <rs
                            key="#Burgi">burgo</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Burgi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1975">Uultiole</placeName> et <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2314"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/83 #places/1974">Climintiano</placeName></geogName> et
                            <rs key="#Castle">Rocka</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/1978"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                            >Senzano</placeName> cum suis pertinentiis, <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2315"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/761">Fereniano</placeName></geogName>, curte in
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2316"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/2733">Corsiniano</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> et <rs key="#Demesnes">terris domnicatis</rs>
                        in <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Demesnes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1976"><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Demesnes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/1540">Cingona</geogName></placeName> et iuxta <rs
                            key="#Rivers">flumen qui vocatur Urcea</rs>, et curte in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1951">Titinano</placeName></geogName>, curte et cella
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">sanctae Mariae qui vocatur <placeName
                                ref="#places/756">Lamule</placeName></orgName> cum suis
                        pertinentiis, curte in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2317"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/2734">Campagnatico</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cella</rs> et <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> in
                            <placeName key="#Curtes #Wine #Cells/hermitages" ref="#places/1944"
                                ><orgName key="#Curtes #Wine #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#juridical_persons/1511"> </orgName></placeName> cum suis <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs> qui vocatur <placeName key="#Wine"
                            ref="#places/2735">Poppae in Cornito</placeName>, <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1515">sanctae Mariae in Ualeriano</orgName> cum
                        ipsis rebus de <geogName ref="#estates/2346"><placeName ref="#places/1964"
                                >Cortitiano</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus adiacentiis et
                        pertinentiis earum, <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cella</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1454">sancti Sauini</orgName> nec non et
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1455">sancti Stephani</orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1452">sanctae Restitutae in <placeName
                                ref="#places/430">Terquino</placeName></orgName>, seu etiam curte
                            <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1950"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1513">sancti Seueri
                                super lacum</orgName></placeName> cum ipsa <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >corticella</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1956">Bisentio</placeName></geogName>, cellam etiam
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1514">sancti <placeName ref="#places/1955"
                                >Miniati</placeName></orgName> nec non et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/308">sancti Salvatoris in <placeName
                                ref="#places/762">valle Racana</placeName></orgName>, curte
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2311"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1970">sancti Petri in Ceruaria</placeName></geogName>
                        cum corticella in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1977"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/1541">Capago</geogName></placeName> cum omnibus rebus
                        et familiis ad eas in integrum pertinentibus vel respicientibus. Denique
                        etiam concedimus ad predictum coenobium omnia <rs key="#Decima">decima</rs>
                        frea et iudiciaria et omnem compositionem et <rs key="#Public_exactions"
                            >exibitionem</rs> pu[b]licam ex omnibus manentibus predicti monasterii
                        ob remedium a[ni]marum nostrarum in usum peregrinorum ad portam monasterii
                        clamantium. Precepimus etiam et statuimus, ut deinceps in futurum haec
                        nostra confirmatio atque donatio a posteris nostris inconvulsa maneat et
                        inlibata, et ut nullus dux marchio comes vicecomes aut ulla regni nostri
                        magna parvaque persona in domos vel res predicti monasterii violentiam
                        inferat aut famulos flagellare vel angariare presumat neque de predictis
                        rebus ullam minorationem facere satagat, sed liceat abbatem sanctamque
                        congregationem predictas cortes et cellas cum eorum integritatibus tenere,
                        omnium inquietudine remota. Si quis hoc nostrum preceptum violare
                        temptaverit, se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras
                            centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamere nostrae</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem sanctae
                            congregationi predicti coenobii</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur et
                        diligentius observetur, manibus propriis corroborantes anuli nostri
                        inpressione subter iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Heinrici (M.) regis
                        invictissimi. Â  <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Everardus"
                                >Eberhardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName><name ref="Uillegis"
                                >Uuilligisi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicapellani</rs> recognovi. Data IIII. idus
                        april. indictione IIII, anno dominicae incarnationis MVI, anno vero domni
                        Heinrici secundi regnantis V; actum <placeName ref="#places/516"
                            >Radesbonae</placeName>. (B. D.)</ab>
                </div>
